title: Great
text: Friendly service. Drinks are cheap. Nice place to relax before a long flight. Highly recommend stopping by.

title: Great
text: Great place! Beer is delicious and reasonably priced. Customer service is absolutely fantastic and friendly.

title: Interesting place
text: This is one interesting place. Worth the drive. Plenty of Soviet equipment on display. Might as well visit during your visa-free stay in Belarus.
place: Sightseeing tour Minsk - Stalin Line Complex

title: The view alone is worth it
text: Right on top of the water...great views of the surf. Beers are cold with decent prices. Service isn't exactly fast, but they are friendly. Great place to relax :)

title: Fantastic !!
text: Maria, at check in, was fantastic. Could not ask for more helpful, friendly, and professional service. Flight was late, so I got to hotel at midnight. She took care of everything and started my holiday off right. Great location, clean rooms, well organized.

title: Must visit !!!
text: Absolutely amazing. Fantastically friendly staff, great food, great prices, and great location. Could not ask for a better place !!!

title: Fantastic
text:
Aram was the best! Friendly and amazing service. The food was fantastic. Truly the best Khinkali in Yerevan! The patio area was clean...the service was timely and friendly.
When you visit, ask for Aram-you won't be disappointed!!

title: The best!
text: Absolutely loved this place! Great service, clean, very comfortable !! Well worth stopping by for a drink.

title: Fantastic
text: Service was excellent...centrally located...within walking distance of plenty of cafes/places to eat and drink. I would recommend staying here on your trip to Minsk. Well worth it and doesn't disappoint.

title: Fantastic Spot
text: Excellent friendly service ! the prices were great, the food even better! Tucked away along the street but well worth stopping by.

title: Fantastic Spot
text: Fantastic service....great view...reasonably priced. Easily one of the best places to pop into for a quick drink :)

title: Meh...
text: Location is great....but the beds and service do NOT match the price you pay to stay here.....The photos posted on TripAdvisor are not accurate...paid for a ocean view terrace and got a sliver of a view of the ocean,. Once again,,,not worth the money,

title: Not what you expect
text:
Sadly, the Semiramis does meet the normal high standard for Intercontinental hotels
No-smoking sections/rooms mean nothing-every one is allowed to smoke where ever they want.
Customer service is almost non-existent. be prepared to wait literally hours to have simple questions answered.

The beds are amazing. and the view of the Nile river is fantastic.

title: Fantastic
text: A must see when visiting the area. The Saqqara Pyramids were great. Not nearly as packed as those in Giza.

title: Pretty Good
text: not the best but not bad either. Busy location but they do a good job getting all the orders handled.

title: Delicious
text: Great place for quick bite. Food was fantastic :) service is great. Plenty of folks pouring in and out.

title: Not bad
text: Live music was great. Beer selection is pretty good. Bartenders were friendly. Not a bad little spot to visit.

title: Meh....
text: happy hour is the only redeeming aspect...over priced in general and not really worth what you pay in any way. service is spot on and the place is nice, but not worth the $$$$$ you're dropping.

title: Best K-BBQ in town
text: Absolutely amazing. best tasting Korean BBQ ive had. service was great. prices were good. I come here every time I am in town.

title: The best
text: First time to Nashville and never left this place. Absolutely fantastic time. Great service...not a bad bar :)

title: Great Views
text: Great way to see the vies of the island. A bit of a walk, but worth it. If you're on the island, you might as well stop by and visit.

title: Tons of history
text: Tons of history. Not nearly as packed as the other tourist attractions. worth adding it to your list of places to visit.

title: Must See
text: Took a taxi-tour from the train station. very educational. interesting to see the Peace Wall after reading/hearing about "the troubles". Worth stopping by.

title: Everything you need
text: Tons of shops and pubs. lots of history. people were fantastic and friendly. Better than expected...

title: Worth It
text: Amazing little bridge. worth the trip. its a bit slippery so be careful, but otherwise a fantastic stop.
place: Old Bridge Area of the Old City of Mostar

title: Stunning
text: Great views...amazing clear water...absolutely beautiful. If you visit the island you ahve to stop by.

title: Great Crew
text: These guys were awesome ! fantastic trip...made sure we had everything we needed. Entertaining the whole time.

title: Bucket List
text: I was a bit stressed leading up it...the lions were much bigger than I imagined...but the guides made me feel completely safe. It was educational and the breakfast was delicious.

title: The Views !!
text: Great views of the lake...nice way to relax in the castle. Coffee was hot and the beer was cold. fantastic.

title: Beautiful !
text: Absolutely beautiful place. If you're near by, you have visit-it was a highlight of my trip to the area.

title: Speechless
text: Absolutely must do if you're in Victoria Falls. The trip was fantastic...safe...the lunch was delicious. Could not have asked for a better experience...in fact I visited Devils Pool twice :)

title: Awesome !
text: You've got to stop by for a cold one. Great micro brews, extremely friendly and helpful staff. Perfect location.

title: Top 5 things to do
text: No reason to NOT take this cruise. About $40...couple hours...free snacks...all-you-can-drink. Breathe-taking sunset. Crocodiles, Giraffe, Hippos...great way to meet folks...simply one of the best things you can do on your vacation. Add it to one of the nights after you get back from a da trip.
place: Shearwater Victoria Falls - Zambezi River Cruises

title: Absolutely fantastic!
text: Hard to beat. The hotel was clean, staff super friendly, and food was great. You are a bit removed from town so be prepared for a shuttle ride to/from. great place to get away. Monkeys, warthogs, and various other animals ALL OVER. simply fantastic.

title: Good Times
text:
It was a long trip but we were able to see a little bit of the northern lights. Our driver was fantastic !!!
We got the pictures from the trip a couples after-which was great !! (see attached photo)
place: Small-Group Aurora Hunt Northern Lights Tour from Tromso

title: Amazing
text: A must see when you visit Budapest. The views are fantastic as well as the architecture. You won't be disappointed.

title: Fantastic !
text: Easily one of the nicest hotels I've ever stayed. You can't beat the location or service. Friendly staff and amazing breakfast. Highly recommended when you visit Budapest. You won't find a nicer place to stay.

title: Awesome!
text: Fantastic service. Great vibe. tons of tvs and plenty of attention from the bartenders. great place to stop by when you're in town.

title: A bit pricey
text: The prices FAR execeeded what you got...easily paying double and tripple the prices for beer and food in the area. Taste great, but not THAT great.

title: Nice place
text:
Location was great...not far from King Street.
Rooms were very nice. Its a brand new hotel so fresh paint and everything is "new". great views of the river. The surrounding construction wasn't fantastic, but it is what it is. overall a great stay.

The restaurant inside (hummingbird) might be the most expensive place I've been-just a heads up.

title: A place to relax
text: Great little bar and restaurant on the water. Great service. Stopped here a couple times for beer and coffee between site-seeing.

title: Fantastic
text: Great location-tons of day trips pick-up at the hotel or across the street. Friendly service, comfy rooms, really impressed. Next door to several restaurants and very close to downtown. No complaints at all.

title: Fantastic
text: Great food. good prices. a nice change from the hotel. Great atmosphere. Worth visiting when you're in town.

title: Great View
text:
Friendly service, great view.
Free shuttle back into town.
Plenty to choose from on the menu.
Not a bad place to stop to/from the border crossing.

title: Must Do This !!
text:
Once in a lifetime...cheap...friendly...easy...safe...

Can't beat it. Highly recommended on your trip to Victoria Falls.

title: Fantastic !
text: Service was great. Prices were great. Fantastic place. The "chicken sticks" were delicious. recommend trying :)

title: Amazing
text: Simply one of the most impressive buidlings ever. the view is fantastic and the drinks/snacks they have available are delicious.

title: Worth it
text: a bit of a walk, but well worth it. The view is unbeatable and the staff are very helpful with directions.

title: Fantastic
text: Could not have asked for a better trip. Plenty of time in all the places we stopped. made the long drive seem easy.

title: Location was great
text: Location and service was fantastic; however, you have to walk up 5 flights of stairs and use four different keys to get to your room from the street. price was a bit expensive for what I got. big room, but A/C "kinda worked", bathroom was tiny, but the bed was large and comfortable. overall, not too bad.

title: Must visit !
text: Fantastic selection of beers....great food...excellent service in a great location. Must stop by when in Kyiv.

title: Luftansa = always late
text: Another two late flights from luftansa....luftansa in german means "perceptually late". What a sham of an airlines.

title: Outstanding !!!
text:
Service was fantastic-more than I could have imagined.
Location is amazing-right next to market.
price was great
dinner was delicious
basically everything I could have asked for was taken care of by this place.

title: Interesting place to see
text: Plenty to see...plenty to do. Every where you look is something new...not a bad place to "people watch" with some coffee.

title: Outstanding experience!
text: Great place. great service. Friendly-patient with my questions about the beers. Must visit for a beer or two or ten.

title: Worth a visit
text: If you're here-go see the towers/gates. well preserved and worth taking a few photos and a short walk from heart of old town

title: Guinness Beef
text: Great Guinness beef. Plenty of tvs for sports. near city center. friendly service. plenty of drinks to choose from

title: lessern known place, but worth a visit
text: La Bella was well listed in tourism sites and didn't pop up on Google, but i walked by it and thought "why not". Good food. worth a visit if you're looking to avoid the crowds.

title: Best place in town
text: One of the best Intercons I have stayed at. Service is spectacular. The breakfast is delicious with plenty of options. The only down side is the hotel gym is small, but it does have an indoor pool. The place is immaculate.

title: A must visit for 1st timers to Kyiv
text: We always bring 1st time visitors to Kyiv to ChaCha bar. great food. great service. not the cheapest place, but its a no-fail for a stangers in the area.
